    <Statements>
      <Statement>Solve real-world and mathematical problems by writing and solving equations of the form &lt;i&gt;x&lt;/i&gt; + &lt;i&gt;p&lt;/i&gt; = &lt;i&gt;q&lt;/i&gt; and&lt;i&gt; px&lt;/i&gt; = &lt;i&gt;q&lt;/i&gt; for cases in which &lt;i&gt;p&lt;/i&gt;, &lt;i&gt;q&lt;/i&gt; and &lt;i&gt;x&lt;/i&gt; are all nonnegative rational numbers.</Statement>
